Notes: LIBRA flow from CT-NA (North America) to FS-EU (Europe).
LIBRA flow from FS-EU (Europe) to XS-AS (Asia).
LIBRA flow from XS-AS (Asia) to CT-OC (Oceania).
LIBRA flow from CT-OC (Oceania) to FS-AF (Africa).
LIBRA flow from FS-AF (Africa) to XS-SA (South America).
LIBRA flow from XS-SA (South America) to CT-NA (North America).
